ut didn't make it in time. Police have not yet determined whether Owens was on drugs at the time. \n The actual shot that killed Owens wasn't shown, but authorities said regardless of what Owens was doing at that moment he was a deadly threat the entire time. \n ", "author": "Associated Press", "title": "Baltimore police show jarring footage of SWAT shooting"}

