r line with those who veer from the day's plans. \n \"Reince has been on a learning curve in the executive branch, he's never been there,\" said Chris Ruddy, a friend of Trump's and among those who have been publicly critical of Priebus. \"There's a settling in that's taken place.\" \n ", "author": "Associated Press", "title": "In Trump's White House drama, Priebus is favorite target"}

